        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Business Supply Chain Transparency on Trafficking and Slavery Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires certain issuers of securities to disclose their efforts to prevent the use of forced labor, slavery, trafficked persons, and child labor in&nbsp;their supply chains. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
